rving bowls, top with gnocchi and garnish with basil leaves, Parmesan shavings and remaining pepper before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["100 g Parmesan cheese, cut into pieces (3 cm), plus extra shaved, to serve","500 g water, plus extra for boiling","500 g carrots, cut into thin rounds (5 mm)","600 g zucchini, cut into cubes (1 cm)","1 egg","2 ½ tsp salt, plus extra to season","250 g plain flour","30 g eschalots","1 garlic clove","30 g olive oil","2 pinches ground black pepper","1 sprig fresh basil, leaves only, for garnishing"]}],"id":"r120358","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-OgZFUltcs-g\/XZM0ORrTiwI\/AAAAAAAAa6I\/yid5FFn-DOscfSUThYvSKzGdN8HpJftzwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_tP5C-zsNr8h7K-8P.png","title":"Carrot gnocchi with zucchini cream","publishedAt":"2016-12-28T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"19.9 g","fat":"17.3 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"54.9 g","calories":"1993 kJ \/ 474 kcal"},"usefulItems":"bowl, thermal serving bowl or other large bowl, piping bag with round nozzle (1 cm), large saucepan, scissors, slotted spoon, stove top","basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h 15m","4 portions"]}